{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I even remember that Bialik came to visit our school, and I presented him with a bouquet of flowers and recited one of his poems.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--translation is that, on the window stood a little dove.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A boy came, and the dove flew away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the boy cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the boy cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's the rough translation of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I suppose that he gave me even-- planted a kiss on my forehead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even so.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't-- I don't remember that anything was imposed, as far as religion is concerned, in our house, except perhaps to use ham on the plate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were allowed to buy ham, particularly if someone was convalescing from a sickness, because ham was considered very nourishing-- on glass plates.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely, but you're not allowed to use the plates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could eat the ham either from the paper, or from a glass plate, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only for health purposes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our maid, I remember, only she could-- she cut the bread roll, and she buttered it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember what thing-- that didn't matter anymore whether she used butter, or she used another sort of fat, and she filled that with ham, and we at it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never brought non-kosher food to school, but that wasn't a problem because none of the kids there would have brought ham to school.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the situation of synagogues or shuls in Poland was such that they were official synagogues.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- I have got, even somewhere, a picture of the grand synagogue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, the owners of big houses considered it a-- a honor and a responsibility to-- to provide a prayer a house for the tenants.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my grandfather made such a provision.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
